title: SAT ACT PSAT 2007 Platinum Edition
description:
Get the scores you need to get into the colleges you want! You have dreams for your future. Kaplan helps you achieve them. We&#039;ve been assisting college-bound men and women since 1938, and we know getting into America&#039;s top colleges has never been more competitive. We&#039;ve assembled this package with all the tools you&#039;ll need to succeed in school; get higher scores on the SAT, ACT, and PSAT*, find the right school for you, and get the money to pay for it!
Features:

    * Disc 1: Higher Score on the SAT & PSAT
      Includes extensive math, critical reading & writing tutorials, 5 full-length SAT simulated tests, 2 full-length PSAT tests, 4 Critical Reading-only section tests,2 regular Math-only section tests, 2 multiple-choice Writing section tests, 2 essay-writing section tests, printable vocabulary lists, and over 700 flashcards.
    * Disk 2: Higher Score on the ACT
      Includes broad content review in English, Math, Reading, and Science, 8 section-length practice tests of the ACT, and 2 full-length practice tests for the ACT.
    * Disk 3-5: Kaplan Essential Review
      Includes critical second look at exam sub-sections, providing supplemental strategies and study materials.
    * Disk 6: Admissions and Tuition Guides
      Includes excerpts from the guidebooks Straight Talk About Paying for College; Parent&#039;s Guide to College Admissions; Procrastinator&#039;s Guide to the ACT
    * Over 3,000 test questions.
    * Exercises to determine where you spend the most time and where you most need improvement.
    * Completed score analysis and performance feedback.
    * Interactive lessons
    * Exam strategies and hints
    * Free New SAT and PSAT practice tests online.

System Requirements:

For PC

    * Windows 98, 98SE, NT 4.0 SP6, 2000, ME, XP
    * Pentium II 300MHz or higher
    * 100MB hard disk space
    * 64MB RAM
    * 640 x 480 screen resolution, thousands of colors
    * Soundblaster-compatible sound card, mouse, speaker
    * 12x CD-ROM or faster
    * Printer (optional)
    * Internet connection (for web features)
